{"tid":771290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"更簿顏色筆引發濾水廠命案","createTime":"2018-08-08T00:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T11:37:49.000Z","uid":81228,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"db70add2c54c4a3f9485795057b57f7e31006b88","tid":771290,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T00:00:32.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】前晚在沙田濾水廠發生的保安員砍殺同事案件，兇案起因原來是為簽更簿的顏色筆問題引起，有人疑一時控制不了情緒釀出命案。被捕58歲姓章疑兇昨午被探員押返現場重組案情，59歲死者吳崇禧的家人往殮房認屍後，帶同道士到現場進行路祭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180807/large/07la6p70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180807%2Flarge%2F07la6p70.jpg&h=851c42d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■疑兇被探員押返現場重組案情。司徒韋桐攝<br />\n<br />\n<strong>為亂放工具瑣事多次爭吵</strong><br />\n<br />\n消息稱，章姓疑兇並無精神病紀錄，但有時行為異常，而他與到濾水廠替工5天任保安員的死者吳崇禧，雖同屬水務署一間外判保安公司，但兩人之前並不認識，惟吳上班僅數天，兩人已為瑣事包括亂放工具多次爭吵，沒料前晚為更簿顏色筆問題爭執後，疑兇涉以斬樹刀砍吳後頸，吳頭顱幾被斬甩斃命。<br />\n<br />\n昨晨9時，死者妻子在女兒、女婿及數名親友的陪同下到富山殮房認屍，下午1時帶同道士到現場路祭，道士在警衞室外做招魂儀式，逗留個多小時離去。<br />\n<br />\n至昨下午4時許，疑兇腰纏鐵鏈及雙手被扣手鐐被探員押返現場重組案情，探員並帶同一個人形公仔在警衞室內，重組當晚案發經過，其後又押他出警衞室，問他是否在閘口附近報警。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁瑞帆、司徒韋桐<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180807/20470554\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180807%2F20470554&d=JnObHxKCxklMoVtFHUMhIi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=2c6937ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180807%2F20470554&h=a084f526\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180807/20470554</a>"},{"pid":"d2fa39c3ff5a7d79e91db85e8999af57a7ffd609","tid":771290,"uid":28279,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T00:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲老屎忽特別外規矩"},{"pid":"3c1ad1c5dce7e78106cb7c056decc2b773382911","tid":771290,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T00:12:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲老屎忽特別多規矩</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ce9ad2ee659c2259f53fa0746e573abeec3a3d8f","tid":771290,"uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T00:17:27.000Z","msg":"劈撚死你！"},{"pid":"948b2b145d9d1a474b3a91f55c6cfd37d3489b4f","tid":771290,"uid":147241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T00:19:12.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0844c195f98c995963f26757f2b70d2518d10e6a","tid":771290,"uid":137604,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T00:20:39.000Z","msg":"從此天下太平，<br />\n不過有新鬼故<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135118609b3e51c941500d3139f6d0ac7162f1e3","tid":771290,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0844c195f98c995963f26757f2b70d2518d10e6a","tid":771290,"uid":137604,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T00:20:39.000Z","msg":"從此天下太平，<br />\n不過有新鬼故<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T00:22:44.000Z","msg":"其他看更以後當夜更實好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8af75188faac09c2b1929cd0c91359efbd3439a","tid":771290,"uid":166288,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T00:25:24.000Z","msg":"痴線 擺明有精神病 <br />\n坐一世監唔好放出黎啦"},{"pid":"528d17686e4edd6153e8b898fe7e554bd5db9df0","tid":771290,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T00:39:18.000Z","msg":"啲躁狂阿伯癲起上嚟真係好恐怖"},{"pid":"4526e4c8a1d77e8404f1229502fcb00ef3938119","tid":771290,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T00:55:36.000Z","msg":"有精神病都做到保安<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm